==Seri==
===Etymology===
Possibly ultimately from Nahuatl ''[[mizton|miztōn]]'' "little puma; cat", from ''[[miztli]]'' "puma" + ''[[-ton#Classical_Nahuatl|-tōn]]'' (diminutive suffix).
===Noun===
'''miist''' (''plural'' '''[[miisatj]]''')

# A [[domestic cat]], ''Felis silvestris catus''.
